final_desc: - Kawat dipilin, tali dan kabel :Kawat dipilin, tali, kabel, ban anyaman, sling dan sejenisnya, dari besi atau baja, tidak diisolasi elektrik.;- Stranded wire, ropes and cables :Stranded wire, ropes, cables, plaited bands, slings and the like, of iron or steel, not electrically insulated.
